Colliers South Africa Says It Expects Its Full-Year Earnings Will Improve

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-09T14:02:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/colliers-south-africa-says-it-expects-its-full-year-earnings-will-improve.html
Colliers South Africa Holdings Ltd. (COL) 
said headline earnings per share from continuing operations for
the 12 months to Feb. 28 are expected to be between 70 percent
and 75 percent better than the headline loss per share reported
a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  